Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:32.32,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}我仿佛从远处听到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:39.65,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}他的眼神中略带寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:44.47,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}再次强烈地感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:51.43,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}这次我飞快地赶到了他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:57.29,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}连一味重复的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:23:03.30,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}和数不胜数的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:08.78,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}也找到了应该追求的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:14.16,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}谁都无法超越这份意志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.27,0:23:21.00,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}只想看到眼前敞开的大千世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:25.33,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}哪怕这只是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:28.19,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}就算会不停迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:32.22,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}梦想也会在内心深处强烈地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:38.55,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}一直一直回响下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:45.03,ED-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}静静地悄悄地闪耀着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:32.32,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}遠くに聞こえた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:39.65,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}彼の目が少し寂しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:44.47,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}もう一度強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:51.43,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}今度は高く駆け抜けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:57.29,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}ただ繰り返す現実も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:23:03.30,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}星の数の願いことも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:08.78,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}目指すべき明日を見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:14.16,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}この思いには勝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.27,0:23:21.00,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}目の前に開かれた果てない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:25.33,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}たとえ夢でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:28.19,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}迷い続けても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:32.22,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}夢の奥で強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:38.55,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}ずっとずっと響いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:45.03,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur6}そっとそっと光ってる
